# TikTok Ads Event Streaming Integration Summary

This documentation details how to set up real-time event streaming from Amplitude to TikTok Ads using the TikTok Events API, enabling marketers to sync first-party behavioral data (like sign-ups, purchases, and engagement events) to improve ad targeting, conversion tracking, and campaign optimization.

